{"id":475582,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":23}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"关于“清官”的歌谣","genre":"文学作品","count":"131","ytitle":"","mtitle":"哪有“清官”顾百姓","ftitle":"","authors":["金铃"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金铃　搜集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官顾官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民顾民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有“清官”顾百姓?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃官饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打官鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打来打去百姓苦!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这两首民谣，流传在浙江金华义乌一带。劳动人民是人类历史的主人，历史上所谓“清官”的真相，他们最了解，这两首民谣不就是历史的有力见证吗!"}]}